topic.title: Self Care Activities - conformance rules

section.p: This template represents a patient's daily self-care ability. These activities are called Activities of Daily Living (ADL) and Instrumental Activities of Daily Living (IADL). ADLs involve caring for and moving of the body (e.g., dressing, bathing, eating). IADLs support an independent life style (e.g., cooking, managing medications, driving, shopping).

ol.li:
SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] templateId ( CONF:1098-28190, CONF:1098-28457 ) such that it
